                     <interp inst="t18020217-72-defend774" type="age" value="30"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18020217-72-off378" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020217-72-off378" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020217-72-off378" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020217-72-cd379" type="crimeDate">8th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020217-72-off378 t18020217-72-cd379"></join>, a pocket-book, value 2d. a handkerchief, value 4d. four papers of garnets and studs, value 1s. and four pawnbroker's duplicates, value 1d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18020217-72-victim775" type="victimName">
                        Isaac 
                        Carcass
                     <interp inst="t18020217-72-victim775" type="surname" value="Carcass"></interp>
